The '''A2216''' is an [[A roads in Great Britain|A road]] in [[South London]].  It runs from [[Denmark Hill]] to [[Sydenham]].  Part of the road is an ancient thoroughfare, [[Lordship Lane (Dulwich)|Lordship Lane]].  In [[Dulwich]] the road [[Concurrency (road)|runs via]] the [[A205 road|South Circular Road]].

