, Postcode, Post code, Postal code... --> |postal_code = |area_code = |website = |footnotes = }}
'''Komodo''' is a village located in the subdistrict of [[Komodo, West Manggarai|Komodo]], [[West Manggarai Regency]], [[East Nusa Tenggara]] province, in [[Indonesia]]. The village encompasses the territory of [[Komodo Island]] and the small surrounding islands.<ref>[https://manggaraibaratkab.bps.go.id/5315backend/pdf_publikasi/Kecamatan-Komodo-Dalam-Angka-2017.pdf Kecamatan Komodo dalam Angka 2017]</ref>
==Population== The native population of Komodo, the [[Komodo people]], has been extinct since the 1980s. The present population consists of [[Bugis|Bugis people]] from [[South Sulawesi]] and [[Bima people]] from [[West Nusa Tenggara]].<ref>[http://sains.kompas.com/read/2013/01/28/15514880/penduduk.hidup.bersama.komodo Penduduk Hidup Bersama Komodo]</ref>
