This is a '''list of [[Europe|European nations]] sorted by their [[Gross Domestic Product]] (GDP)''', the value of all final goods and services produced within a nation in a given year. The GDP dollar estimates presented here are derived from [[purchasing power parity]] (PPP) calculations for the latest years recorded in the [[CIA World Factbook]]. The list includes all members of the [[Council of Europe]], Belarus and Kosovo. The figures provided are all quoted in [[United States dollar|US dollars]].

